# Dev-only artifacts — kept in local working tree, not published to GitHub.
# Internal planning docs, design specs, and legacy v1/v2 reference code
# are useful during development but shouldn't appear in the public repo
# file tree. Keeping them gitignored preserves the local working copy
# while ensuring they stay out of commits, PRs, and GitHub Pages.
